OL,3,CMan jailed for string of sex offences
OL,4,Ccommitted in the 1990s
OL,6,FA Cardiff man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fhistorical child sexual offences
OL,8,Fcommitted in the 1990s.
OL,10,FPeter White, 63, of Fairwater,
OL,11,FCardiff, appeared at Cardiff Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Thursday, July 25, where he
OL,13,Fwas jailed for 38 months.
OL,15,FHis victim came forward decades later
OL,16,Fin 2021.
OL,18,FHe had previously been found guilty of
OL,19,Ffive counts of gross indecency
OL,20,Ffollowing a trial.
