OL,6,FWhite was made subject of a
OL,7,FRestraining Order, prohibiting him
OL,8,Ffrom contacting the victim in any way
OL,9,Fonline, and a 10-year Sexual Harm
OL,10,FPrevention Order was also issued.
OL,12,FThe court heard how he groomed his
OL,13,Fvictim, who came forward decades later
OL,14,Fin 2021 to report his crimes.
