OL,3,CMan jailed for string of sex offences
OL,4,Ccommitted in the 1990s
OL,6,FSteve Gunney, from the Rape
OL,7,FInvestigation Team, said: "The victim
OL,8,Fin this case has shown tremendous
OL,9,Fcourage to come forward. She has
OL,10,Fendured a long and difficult process
OL,11,Fbut got through it with invaluable
OL,12,Fsupport from an Independent Sexual
OL,13,FViolence Adviser (ISVA).
OL,15,F"This conviction and sentence is yet
OL,16,Fanother example of why it is never too
OL,17,Flate for victims of sexual offences to
OL,18,Fcome forward. We will listen to
OL,19,Fvictims and fully support them along
OL,20,Fthe way.
